            "format": "basic_html",
            "processed": "<p><span>Trace ridges combines filtering, Watershed transforms, Edge detection and mathematical morphology to trace ridges in an image with fibre-like structures.&nbsp;</span><br><span>Publication provides objective comparison of six existing methodologies (Edge detection, CT Fire, Scale Space, Twombli, U-Net and Graph Based).</span></p>",
